| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2021-1347 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 85fbd80d-5a5a-54e5-8c6c-361734c3aaa9"
